# No AI Meta-Mention Policy

Never use "cursor", "agent", or "IA" (or variants) in:

- Commit messages.
- PR titles or descriptions.
- Jira ticket titles, descriptions, or comments.
- Branch names.
- Any other artifact or metadata produced by the workflow.

Use neutral, human-authored wording instead.
